{"id":"6c63dc2e-6083-40d2-9900-d2831dc5deae","name":"Sadayo Kawakami, Your Homeroom Teacher","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>\"I-I always come here when I want to unwind. Adults need to relax, too. We have many responsibilities...\"</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Sadayo Kawakami is your homeroom teacher at Shujin Academy. Laid-back, understanding, and with a hint of self-loathing, Ms. Kawakami aims to be a competent member of her workplace. She's not entirely squeaky clean, though, as you may by chance come across her during the night hours moonlighting as the maid who's a bit over the hill for her line of work, 'Becky'.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Appears in </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(192, 3, 3)\"><strong><em>Persona 5</em>.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">(Pretty sure site rules force me to make this bot limitless, due to what \"services\" her maid job provides.)</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(183, 183, 183)\">(Please leave reviews if I can improve the character or if you enjoy the character. Your ratings give me endorphins.)</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><hr><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255)\"><strong><em>RECOMMENDED BOT LINKS:</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/485a170a-d082-4bc2-8378-be4e826d059c_character-futaba-sakura\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255)\"><strong>Futaba Sakura</strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255)\">